{"tid":2514357,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"首位官中通識科教師被釘牌 學生批文革再臨 不敢校內論政：學校話唔畀再講","createTime":"2021-05-03T08:09:17.000Z","updateTime":"2021-05-03T22:42:42.000Z","uid":130626,"like":8,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"425ae2800ad3bf5b613ccc385b3e1e9a5b97027e","tid":2514357,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T08:09:17.000Z","msg":"龍翔官立中學通識科前教師被指「挑起學生對國家、中國人民的反感」，遭教育局「釘牌」。有曾被其任教的學生稱他是「好好嘅老師」，愛錫學生，授課不偏頗，卻突然被DQ，批評事件是「無中生有」和「搞緊文革」。<br />\n<br />\n黃同學表示，老師在課堂上「最敏感」是講過六四事件，也只是讓學生看當年相片和片段，告訴學生當年發生的事，讓學生自行分析。黃補充，該老師平日教學「好中立」，不會牽涉「顏色」，教學多用《鏗鏘集》等港台片段，讓學生思考，「幾多人鍾意佢」。<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210503/BAPJFP3AQZCOVAYV2Y7KS7PVIM/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210503%2FBAPJFP3AQZCOVAYV2Y7KS7PVIM%2F&d=xOzWlad5M6duuHBPObmdOOrkGmmZttFFipzpmUasbQ8%3D&h=77d632d8\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210503%2FBAPJFP3AQZCOVAYV2Y7KS7PVIM%2F&h=43d5cb36\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210503/BAPJFP3AQZCOVAYV2Y7KS7PVIM/</a>"},{"pid":"f9232e2c30385bf7c8a48148d210a896a6ebe2e7","tid":2514357,"uid":155095,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T08:10:47.000Z","msg":"唔跟中共死硬 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static01-proxy.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/2230000/2231923/1217_1024.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic01-proxy.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2230000%2F2231923%2F1217_1024.png&h=87356a06&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a2634cf5552dbe65bb5c1f69f7957aadf12283f7","tid":2514357,"uid":230530,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T08:12:49.000Z","msg":"垃圾學校 全黃大仙最垃圾個間"},{"pid":"a30df4dcc1308201a61d55fff349dbce0e261e93","tid":2514357,"uid":155095,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a2634cf5552dbe65bb5c1f69